But SCP-1037 only affects non-biological material, so given that the Sarkics make everything  from organic material, it would have no effect on them, right? Or am I missing something here?

Based on its effect I would have assumed that it was used as a weapon against the Church of the Broken God and its mechanical creations and not as a weapon created by them to fight the Sarkics.

And now that I think about it, how does it affect the gelatin in which it was originally contained? Gelatin is made from animal skin and bones and should therefore not be affected by SCP-1037, if it only affect non-biological materials.







